the effects this has on the photoionisation modelling of the\nwarm absorber. We show how the assumed SEDs influence the thermal stability of\neach phase and whether or not the two absorber phases in ESO 113-G010 can\nco-exist in pressure equilibrium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2012 20:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
