proach and how well it fares as regards the various\nfacets of the Problem of Time and as an implementation of QM propositions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2012 03:11:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Aug 2012 11:19:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
